hwL2vpnOamTrap.name: hwL2vpnOamTrap

revisions.description: V2.04, add hwL2vpnOamTunnelNonSupport, hwL2vpnOamTunnelNonSupportResumed for router.
V2.02, add hwL2vpnOamFdi, hwL2vpnOamFdiClear for PTN5900.
V2.01, add hwL2vpnOamSd1Far, hwL2vpnOamSd1FarClear, hwL2vpnOamSd2Far, hwL2vpnOamSd2FarClear for far-end packet loss.

hwL2vpnOamTrap.contactinfo: Huawei Industrial Base Bantian, Longgang Shenzhen 518129 People's Republic of China Website: http://www.huawei.com Email: support@huawei.com
hwL2vpnOamTrap.description: The HUAWEI-L2VPN-OAM-MIB contains objects to manage OAM TRAP.

hwL2vpnServiceType.name: hwL2vpnServiceType
hwL2vpnServiceType.description: This object indicates the classification(vpws or vpls) of the PW.

hwL2vpnProtocolType.name: hwL2vpnProtocolType
hwL2vpnProtocolType.description: This object indicates the protocol(static or ldp or bgp) of one PW's classification.

hwL2vpnVcID.name: hwL2vpnVcID
hwL2vpnVcID.description: This object indicates the ID of the PW. This object should contain a value of zero if not valid.

hwL2vpnVcType.name: hwL2vpnVcType
hwL2vpnVcType.description: This object indicates the type of the PW. This object should contain a value of zero if not valid.

hwL2vpnPeerAddr.name: hwL2vpnPeerAddr
hwL2vpnPeerAddr.description: This object contain the value of the peer node address of the PW/PE maintenance protocol entity. This object should contain a value of all zeroes if not applicable

hwL2vpnIfIndex.name: hwL2vpnIfIndex
hwL2vpnIfIndex.description: This object indicates the index of the AC interface. This object should contain a value of zero if not valid.

hwL2vpnPwMaster.name: hwL2vpnPwMaster
hwL2vpnPwMaster.description: This object indicates the role (primary or second) of the PW. This object should contain a value of zero if not valid.

hwL2vpnRmtSiteID.name: hwL2vpnRmtSiteID
hwL2vpnRmtSiteID.description: This object indicates the Route Distinguisher. This object should contain a value of zero if not valid.

hwL2vpnInLabel.name: hwL2vpnInLabel
hwL2vpnInLabel.description: This object indicates the received label be used in PW. This object should contain a value of zero if not valid.

hwL2vpnOutLabel.name: hwL2vpnOutLabel
hwL2vpnOutLabel.description: This object indicates the transfer label be used in pw. This object should contain a value of zero if not valid.

hwL2vpnIfName.name: hwL2vpnIfName
hwL2vpnIfName.description: This object indicates the AC interface's name. This object should contain a value of null if not valid.

hwL2vpnVsiName.name: hwL2vpnVsiName
hwL2vpnVsiName.description: This object indicates the the vsi's name. This object should contain a value of null if not valid.

hwL2vpnOamType.name: hwL2vpnOamType
hwL2vpnOamType.description: This object indicates the type (MPLS OAM or MPLS-TP OAM) of the OAM. This object should contain a value of zero if not valid.

hwL2vpnOamDloc.name: hwL2vpnOamDloc
hwL2vpnOamDloc.description: OAM reported an alarm about PW disconnection.

hwL2vpnOamDlocClear.name: hwL2vpnOamDlocClear
hwL2vpnOamDlocClear.description: OAM reported the clearing of the dLOC alarm.

hwL2vpnOamSd1Near.name: hwL2vpnOamSd1Near
hwL2vpnOamSd1Near.description: OAM reported an alarm about the near-end packet loss exceeding sd1.

hwL2vpnOamSd1NearClear.name: hwL2vpnOamSd1NearClear
hwL2vpnOamSd1NearClear.description: OAM reported an alarm about the near-end packet loss dropping below sd1.

hwL2vpnOamRdi.name: hwL2vpnOamRdi
hwL2vpnOamRdi.description: OAM reported an alarm about a remote defect.

hwL2vpnOamRdiClear.name: hwL2vpnOamRdiClear
hwL2vpnOamRdiClear.description: OAM reported an alarm about the removal of the remote defect.

hwL2vpnOamMeg.name: hwL2vpnOamMeg
hwL2vpnOamMeg.description: OAM reported an unexpected MEG alarm.

hwL2vpnOamMegClear.name: hwL2vpnOamMegClear
hwL2vpnOamMegClear.description: OAM reported the clearing of the unexpected MEG alarm

hwL2vpnOamMep.name: hwL2vpnOamMep
hwL2vpnOamMep.description: OAM reported an unexpected MEP alarm.

hwL2vpnOamMepClear.name: hwL2vpnOamMepClear
hwL2vpnOamMepClear.description: OAM reported an alarm about the clearing of the unexpected MEP alarm.

hwL2vpnOamPeriod.name: hwL2vpnOamPeriod
hwL2vpnOamPeriod.description: OAM reported an alarm about an unexpected CV packet period.

hwL2vpnOamPeriodClear.name: hwL2vpnOamPeriodClear
hwL2vpnOamPeriodClear.description: OAM reported an alarm about the rectification of the unexpected CV packet period.

hwL2vpnOamAisClear.name: hwL2vpnOamAisClear
hwL2vpnOamAisClear.description: OAM reported the clearing of the AIS alarm.

hwL2vpnOamSd2Near.name: hwL2vpnOamSd2Near
hwL2vpnOamSd2Near.description: OAM reported an alarm about the near-end packet loss exceeding sd2.

hwL2vpnOamSd2NearClear.name: hwL2vpnOamSd2NearClear
hwL2vpnOamSd2NearClear.description: OAM reported an alarm indicating the near-end packet loss dropping below sd2.

hwL2vpnOamLck.name: hwL2vpnOamLck
hwL2vpnOamLck.description: OAM reported a PW service layers LCK alarm.

hwL2vpnOamLckClear.name: hwL2vpnOamLckClear
hwL2vpnOamLckClear.description: OAM reported the PW service layers LCK alarm disappearance.

hwL2vpnOamCsfClear.name: hwL2vpnOamCsfClear
hwL2vpnOamCsfClear.description: OAM reported the CSF alarm disappearance.

hwL2vpnOamExcess.name: hwL2vpnOamExcess
hwL2vpnOamExcess.description: OAM reported a TTSI excess alarm.

hwL2vpnOamExcessClear.name: hwL2vpnOamExcessClear
hwL2vpnOamExcessClear.description: OAM reported the TTSI excess alarm disappearance.

hwL2vpnOamMismatch.name: hwL2vpnOamMismatch
hwL2vpnOamMismatch.description: OAM reported a TTSI mismatch alarm.

hwL2vpnOamMismatchClear.name: hwL2vpnOamMismatchClear
hwL2vpnOamMismatchClear.description: OAM reported the TTSI mismatch alarm disappearance.

hwL2vpnOamMismerge.name: hwL2vpnOamMismerge
hwL2vpnOamMismerge.description: OAM reported a TTSI mismerge alarm.

hwL2vpnOamMismergeClear.name: hwL2vpnOamMismergeClear
hwL2vpnOamMismergeClear.description: OAM reported the TTSI mismerge alarm disappearance.

hwL2vpnOamFailClear.name: hwL2vpnOamFailClear
hwL2vpnOamFailClear.description: OAM reported the failed-negotiation alarm disappearance.

hwL2vpnOamDbdiClear.name: hwL2vpnOamDbdiClear
hwL2vpnOamDbdiClear.description: OAM reported the DBDI alarm disappearance.

hwL2vpnOamUnknown.name: hwL2vpnOamUnknown
hwL2vpnOamUnknown.description: OAM reported an unknown limitation alarm.

hwL2vpnOamUnknownClear.name: hwL2vpnOamUnknownClear
hwL2vpnOamUnknownClear.description: OAM reported the unknown limitation alarm disappearance.

hwL2vpnOamLocalLock.name: hwL2vpnOamLocalLock
hwL2vpnOamLocalLock.description: OAM reported a local PW LOCK alarm.

hwL2vpnOamLocalLockClear.name: hwL2vpnOamLocalLockClear
hwL2vpnOamLocalLockClear.description: OAM reported the local LOCK PW alarm disappearance.

hwL2vpnOamSd1Far.description: OAM reported an alarm about the far-end packet loss exceeding sd1.

hwL2vpnOamSd1FarClear.name: hwL2vpnOamSd1FarClear
hwL2vpnOamSd1FarClear.description: OAM reported an alarm indicating the far-end packet loss dropping below sd1.

hwL2vpnOamSd2Far.name: hwL2vpnOamSd2Far
hwL2vpnOamSd2Far.description: OAM reported an alarm about the far-end packet loss exceeding sd2.

hwL2vpnOamSd2FarClear.name: hwL2vpnOamSd2FarClear
hwL2vpnOamSd2FarClear.description: OAM reported an alarm indicating the far-end packet loss dropping below sd2.

hwL2vpnOamFdiClear.description: OAM reported the FDI alarm disappearance.

hwL2vpnOamTunnelNonSupport.name: hwL2vpnOamTunnelNonSupport
hwL2vpnOamTunnelNonSupport.description: OAM for PW does not support the current public tunnel.

hwL2vpnOamTunnelNonSupportResumed.description: The alarm that OAM for PW does not support the current public tunnel is resumed.
